            <h3><i class="bi bi-list-check me-2"></i>Étapes back-end (timeline)</h3>
            <span class="badge-soft">LoA 2 / LoA 3</span>
          </div>

          <div class="timeline">
            <div class="t-item">
              <div class="t-top">
                <b>0) Session & consentement</b>
                <span class="code">POST <span class="kbd">/eid/session/start</span></span>
              </div>
              <p>Création <span class="kbd">session_id</span>, affichage notice, consentement explicite, paramètres LoA & timeout.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="t-item">
              <div class="t-top">
                <b>1) Pré-lookup (pré-KYC)</b>
                <span class="code">POST <span class="kbd">/eid/session/prelookup</span></span>
              </div>
              <p>Entrées : last4 téléphone + DOB → retour <span class="kbd">candidate_set</span> (0..N) ou "nouveau client".</p>
            </div>

            <div class="t-item">
              <div class="t-top">
                <b>2) Upload + contrôle qualité</b>
                <span class="code">POST <span class="kbd">/eid/session/{id}/upload</span></span>
              </div>
              <p>Capture recto/verso → vérif netteté/reflets/recadrage → rejet si illisible (reprise guidée).</p>
            </div>

            <div class="t-item">
              <div class="t-top">
                <b>3) OCR & extraction biodata</b>
                <span class="code">POST <span class="kbd">/eid/session/{id}/ocr</span></span>
              </div>
              <p>Extraction : type doc, <b>N#</b>, noms, DOB, nationalité, expiration, MRZ si passeport, confiance OCR.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="t-item">
              <div class="t-top">
                <b>4) Matching "100%" + tolérances contrôlées</b>
                <span class="code">POST <span class="kbd">/eid/session/{id}/match</span></span>
              </div>
              <p>
                Couche 1 : match strict <b>N# exact</b> + DOB exact + noms normalisés.<br/>
                Couche 2 : variations typographiques sur noms uniquement (jamais sur N#). Sorties : EXACT / PARTIAL / NO_MATCH / DUPLICATE_RISK.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="t-item">
              <div class="t-top">
                <b>5) Comparaison OCR historiques</b>
                <span class="code">POST <span class="kbd">/eid/session/{id}/history-check</span></span>
              </div>
              <p>Empreintes : <span class="kbd">doc_hash</span> + <span class="kbd">ocr_fingerprint</span> → divergence = <b>FLAG_REVIEW</b> (revue humaine).</p>
            </div>

            <div class="t-item">
              <div class="t-top">
                <b>6) IA (signaux) sous gouvernance</b>
                <span class="code">POST <span class="kbd">/eid/session/{id}/ai-signals</span></span>
              </div>
              <p>Ollama génère annotations/signaux ; Qdrant indexe similarités. Si blocage/doute → <b>revue humaine obligatoire</b>.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="t-item mb-0">
              <div class="t-top">
                <b>7) Evidence Pack (preuve probante)</b>
                <span class="code">POST <span class="kbd">/eid/session/{id}/evidence</span></span>
              </div>
              <p>Paquet scellé : hashes, logs, OCR, résultats match, horodatage, signature/scellement (HSM), archivage (WORM/coffre-fort).</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="hint mt-3">
            Les ID POS suivent le même protocole : l'UX est plus courte, les captures se font via caméra/scan du terminal.
